Compressing High Dynamic Range (HDR) colors to Standard Dynamic Range (SDR) space:

```hlsl
// HLSL Tone mapping shader snippet
float3 ReinhardToneMap(float3 HDRColor) {
    // Formula: Color = Color / (Color + 1)
    float3 LDRColor = HDRColor / (HDRColor + float3(1.0f, 1.0f, 1.0f));
    return LDRColor;
}
```
